 "remarks": "Located in the desirable Greenbriar complex on Summer Street in Stamford, this 2nd and 3rd floor townhouse style condominium offers spacious living with convenient access to downtown, shopping, dining, Metro-North, and Scalzi Park. This 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath unit features a clean and functional layout with generously sized rooms, abundant storage, and reserved garage parking.  The main level includes a full kitchen with dining area open to the living room, fireplace, half bath, and a bright sunroom offering additional living space and natural light. The upper level features two spacious bedroom suites, each with its own full bathroom, providing flexibility and privacy for a variety of living arrangements. Modern finishes throughout offer a neutral backdrop ready for personal touches. Schedule your showing today.",
